    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this extraordinary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom-preserved condition, exhibiting a flawless aesthetic and mechanical integrity that demands the attention of the most discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine interior appointments to the lustrous exterior finish, underscores a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. This is an unparalleled opportunity to acquire a definitive example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
