      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 straight-six, benefitting from a documented VANOS overhaul and preventative rod bearing replacement with VAC Motorsports treated bearings. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power to a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is structurally immaculate, having undergone a proactive subframe reinforcement. Suspension kinematics are sharp, utilizing fresh bushings and OEM-spec DampTronic dampers. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero clear coat failure, while the interior leather shows no bolster wear or UV degradation. A mechanically synchronized, turn-key specimen for the purist.",
